cradio
======
A very basic TUI wrapper around mpv with vi-like bindings using termbox2.
Reads from a stations list formatted as:

    "<name>" "<url>"
    "<name>" "<url>"

WIP.


Requirements
------------
POSIX environment
mpv header files


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk if needed (/usr/local namespace by default).
Build and install (if necessary as root) using:

    make clean install


Documentation
-------------
View man page for additional usage information.
